**Ice Prince** | Solo Miscellaneous - Ice Royals | Limited
__Basics__
The Ice Prince wins with the ice royals and joins a channel with them to communicate securely.
__Details__
The Ice Prince does not have any special abilities. If somebody tries to copy an ice royal an Ice Prince is created instead. 
Frozen players are obstructed; if they have an investigative power and are affected by obstructions, they will see the Ice Prince as a role the Ice Prince chooses at the start of the game. 
The Ice Prince is an ice royal, knows the other ice royals and works together with them. The ice royals win when all players, except the ice royals, are frozen or dead.

__Simplified__
The Ice Prince wins with the ice royals and joins a channel with them to communicate securely.
